<h1 id="hllcæ³•">HLLCæ³•</h1>

<p>ã“ã“ã§ã¯(ç£æ°—)æµä½“åŠ›å­¦ã®è¨ˆç®—æ‰‹æ³•ã§ã‚ã‚‹HLLCæ³•ã«ã¤ã„ã¦ã®å‹‰å¼·ãƒ¡ãƒ¢ã‚’è¨˜è¿°ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="æµä½“æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ç¾¤">æµä½“æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ç¾¤</h2>

<p>ã„ããªã‚Šç£å ´ãŒã‚ã‚‹å ´åˆã¯é›£ã—ã„ãŸã‚ã€æœ€åˆã¯ç£å ´ã®ãªã„æµä½“ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ç°¡å˜ã®ãŸã‚1æ¬¡å…ƒç³»ã‚’è§£ãã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨è§£ããŸã„æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial}{\partial t} \left( \begin{array}{c}
\rho \\
\rho v_x \\
\rho v_y \\
\rho v_z \\
E
\end{array} \right) + \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( \begin{array}{c} 
\rho v_x \\
\rho v_x v_x + P \\
\rho v_y v_x \\
\rho v_z v_x \\
(E + P) v_x
\end{array}\right) 
= \frac{\partial \mathbf{U}}{\partial t} + \frac{\partial \mathbf{F}}{\partial x} 
= \mathbf{0} \tag{1}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‹ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="æµæŸè¨ˆç®—">æµæŸè¨ˆç®—</h3>

<p><a href="/simulation/hll">HLL (Harten-Lax-van Leer)æ³•</a>ã¯ã€ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã‚’1ã¤ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ä»®å®šã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ä»Šå›ã¯ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã‚’ä¸‹å›³ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«2ã¤ã¨ã—ã¦è¨ˆç®—ã‚’è¡Œã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/simulation/hllc_01.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>ãŸã ã—ã€ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã«ãŠã„ã¦ã€\(x\)æ–¹å‘ã®æµä½“ã®é€Ÿåº¦ã¯ä¸€å®šã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ãªã‚ã¡</p>

\[v_{x, L}^\ast = v_{x, R}^\ast = S_M \tag{2}\]

<p>ã“ã®\(S_M\)ã¯ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã‚’ä»£è¡¨ã™ã‚‹é€Ÿåº¦ã§ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦<a href="/simulation/hll">HLLã®ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹</a></p>

\[\mathbf{U}_\mathrm{HLL}^\ast 
= \frac{S_R \mathbf{U}_R - S_L \mathbf{U}_L - \mathbf{F}_R + \mathbf{F}_L}{S_R - S_L} \tag{3}\]

<p>ã‹ã‚‰å°å‡ºã•ã‚Œã‚‹ã ã‚ã†ã¨è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\rho_\mathrm{HLL}^\ast 
= \frac{S_R \rho_R - S_L \rho_L - \rho_R v_{x, R} + \rho_L v_{x, L}}{S_R - S_L}\]

\[(\rho v_x)_\mathrm{HLL}^\ast 
= \frac{S_R \rho_R v_{x, R} - S_L \rho_L v_{x, L} - (\rho_R v_{x, R} v_{x, R} + P_R) + (\rho_L v_{x, L} v_{x, L} + P_L)}{S_R - S_L}\]

<p>ä»¥ä¸Šã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[S_M 
= \frac{(\rho v_x)_\mathrm{HLL}^\ast}{\rho_\mathrm{HLL}^\ast} 
= \frac{(S_R - v_{x, R}) \rho_R v_{x, R} - (S_L - v_{x, L}) v_{x, L} - P_R + P_L}{(S_R - v_{x, R})\rho_R - -(S_L-v_{x, L}) \rho_L} \tag{4}\]

<p>ã¨æ±‚ã¾ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚æ¬¡ã«ä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã®åœ§åŠ›ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚\(S_\alpha \ (\alpha = L, R)\)ã®é€Ÿåº¦ã§é€²ã‚€æ³¢é¢ã§ã®ã‚¸ãƒ£ãƒ³ãƒ—æ¡ä»¶ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[S_\alpha \mathbf{U}_\alpha^\ast - \mathbf{F}_\alpha^\ast 
= S_\alpha \mathbf{U}_\alpha - \mathbf{F}_\alpha \tag{5}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã®å¼ã¨(1)å¼ã®ç¬¬1å¼(<a href="/mhd/continuity">é€£ç¶šã®å¼</a>)ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[S_\alpha \rho_\alpha^\ast - \rho_\alpha^\ast v_{x, \alpha}^\ast 
= S_\alpha \rho_\alpha - \rho_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} \ \underbrace{\Longrightarrow}_{(2)} \ 
\rho_\alpha^\ast 
= \rho_\alpha \frac{S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}}{S_\alpha - S_M} \tag{6}\]

<p>ç¶šã„ã¦(5)å¼ã¨(1)å¼ã®ç¬¬2å¼(<a href="/mhd/momentum">\(x\)æ–¹å‘ã®é‹å‹•é‡ä¿å­˜å¼</a>)ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
&amp;S_\alpha \rho_\alpha^\ast v_{x, \alpha}^\ast - (\rho_\alpha^\ast v_{x, \alpha}^\ast v_{x, \alpha}^\ast + P_\alpha^\ast) 
= S_\alpha \rho_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} - (\rho_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} v_{x, \alpha} + P_\alpha) \\
&amp;\underbrace{\Longrightarrow}_{(2)} \ 
\rho_\alpha^\ast S_M (S_\alpha - S_M) - P_\alpha^\ast 
= \rho_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} (S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}) - P_\alpha
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã“ã“ã«(6)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\rho_\alpha S_M (S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}) - P_\alpha^\ast 
= \rho_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} (S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}) - P_\alpha \ \Longrightarrow \ 
P_\alpha^\ast 
= P_\alpha + \rho_\alpha (S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}) (S_M - v_{x, \alpha}) \tag{7}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚å®Ÿã¯è¡æ’ƒæ³¢ç®¡ã®ç‰©ç†ã‹ã‚‰ã€\(S_M\)ã‚’æŒŸã‚“ã§</p>

\[P_L^\ast = P_R^\ast = P^\ast \tag{8}\]

<p>ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã¯\(\rho_L^\ast \neq \rho_R^\ast\)ã§ã‚ã‚ŠãªãŒã‚‰åœ§åŠ›ã¯åŒã˜å€¤ã§ãƒãƒ©ãƒ³ã‚¹ã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹æ¥è§¦ä¸é€£ç¶šé¢ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’æ„å‘³ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
åŒæ§˜ã«(1)å¼ã®ç¬¬3å¼(<a href="/mhd/momentum">\(y\)æ–¹å‘ã®é‹å‹•é‡ä¿å­˜å¼</a>)ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[S_\alpha \rho_\alpha^\ast v_{y, \alpha}^\ast - \rho_\alpha^\ast v_{y, \alpha}^\ast v_{x, \alpha}^\ast 
= S_\alpha \rho_\alpha v_{y, \alpha} - \rho_\alpha v_{y, \alpha} v_{x, \alpha} \ \underbrace{\Longrightarrow}_{(2)} \ 
\rho_\alpha^\ast v_{y, \alpha}^\ast (S_\alpha - S_M) 
= \rho_\alpha v_{y, \alpha} (S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha})\]

<p>ã“ã“ã«(6)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§</p>

\[v_{y, \alpha}^\ast 
= v_{y, \alpha} \tag{9}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚åŒæ§˜ã«</p>

\[v_{z, \alpha}^\ast 
= v_{z, \alpha} \tag{10}\]

<p>ã‚‚å°ãã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚æœ€å¾Œã«(1)å¼ã¨ç¬¬5å¼(<a href="/mhd/energy">ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼ä¿å­˜å¼</a>)ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[S_\alpha E_\alpha^\ast - (E_\alpha^\ast + \underbrace{P_\alpha^\ast}_{(8)}) \underbrace{v_{x, \alpha}^\ast}_{(2)} 
= S_\alpha E_\alpha - (E_\alpha + P_\alpha) v_{x, \alpha} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
E_\alpha^\ast 
= \frac{(S_\alpha - v_{x, \alpha}) E_\alpha - P_\alpha v_{x, \alpha} + P^\ast S_M}{S_\alpha - S_M} \tag{11}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã‚‰ã‚’ã¾ã¨ã‚ã¦</p>

\[\mathbf{F}_\alpha^\ast 
= \left( \begin{array}{c} 
\rho_\alpha^\ast S_M \\
\rho_\alpha^\ast S_M S_M + P^\ast \\
\rho_\alpha^\ast v_{y, \alpha}^\ast S_M \\
\rho_\alpha^\ast v_{z, \alpha}^\ast S_M \\
(E_\alpha^\ast + P^\ast) S_M
\end{array}\right) \tag{12}\]

<p>ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§ã€æ±‚ã‚ãŸã‹ã£ãŸä¸­é–“çŠ¶æ…‹ã®æµæŸã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚é€”ä¸­ã§å‡ºã¦ããŸã‚ˆã†ã«ã€HLLCæ³•ã¯æ¥è§¦ä¸é€£ç¶šé¢ã®æ³¢ã®é€Ÿåº¦\(S_M\)ãŠã‚ˆã³ãã‚Œã‚’å¢ƒã«ç‰©ç†é‡ã®å¤‰åŒ–ãŒèµ·ã“ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’è€ƒæ…®ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚
HLLCã®â€Câ€ã¯ã€HLLã‚’æ”¹è‰¯ã—æ¥è§¦ä¸é€£ç¶šé¢(contact discontinuity)ã‚‚æ‰ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«ã—ãŸã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰æ¥ã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ã«ç”¨ã„ã‚‹">æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ã«ç”¨ã„ã‚‹</h3>

<p><a href="/simulation/hll">HLLæ³•</a>ã¨åŒæ§˜ã«ã€å®Ÿéš›ã®æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ã§ã¯\(S_L, S_M, S_R\)ã®å¤§ãã•ã‚’è€ƒæ…®ã™ã‚‹å¿…è¦ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚HLLã®ã¨ãã¨åŒæ§˜ã«è€ƒãˆã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ä¸‹å›³ã¯å·¦ä¸Šã‹ã‚‰é †ã«\(S_L &gt; 0, S_L \leq 0 &lt; S_M, S_M \leq 0 &lt;S_R, S_R \leq 0\)ã®å ´åˆã‚’å›³ç¤ºã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/simulation/hllc_02.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>ä»¥ä¸Šã‚ˆã‚Šã€æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ã‚’è¡Œã†å ´åˆã€ãã®æµæŸã®é¸æŠã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{F}_\mathrm{HLL} 
= \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} 
\mathbf{F}_L &amp; \mathrm{if} \ S_L &gt; 0 \\
\mathbf{F}_L^\ast &amp; \mathrm{if} \ S_L \leq 0 &lt; S_M \\
\mathbf{F}_R^\ast &amp; \mathrm{if} \ S_M \leq 0 &lt; S_R \\
\mathbf{F}_R &amp; \mathrm{if} \ S_R \leq 0
\end{array}\right. \tag{13}\]

<script async="" src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9131160172347693" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

